<div><div class="description"></div><h1>Schemas</h1><div class="panel panel-default"><div class="panel-body"><p>The schema provides more detailed information about the properties of a resource.
The schema is represented by a dictionary containing names of resource properties as keys
and objects describing the corresponding property as values.
These objects are called <strong>field schema</strong> and form the core of the schema representation,
each of them can contain its own <code>_links</code> and <code>_embedded</code> section.</p>
