<td>The value of the property must at least contain the specified amount of characters</td>
<td>Integer</td>
<td>0</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:center">maxLength</td>
<td>The value of the property must at most contain the specified amount of characters</td>
<td>Integer</td>
<td>∞</td>
</tr>
<tr>
